			</BitmapImage>
			<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_7.png')" x="303" y="1069" blendMode="normal">
			</BitmapImage>
			<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_8.png')" x="244" y="1069" blendMode="normal">
			</BitmapImage>
			<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_9.png')" x="424" y="1069" blendMode="normal">
			</BitmapImage>
			<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_10.png')" x="124" y="1069" blendMode="normal">
			</BitmapImage>
			<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_11.png')" x="66" y="1069" blendMode="normal">
			</BitmapImage>
			<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_13.png')" x="486" y="1069">
			</BitmapImage>
		</Group>
		<RichText x="739" y="223" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">开局入战时，站在石台上的督军突然跃下，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">50%</span><span>伤害。本技能仅督军位于石台雕像状态下，开局入战施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_14.png')" x="720" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_15.png')" x="1392" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1393" y="393">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_17.png')" x="1391" y="681">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_18.png')" x="1393" y="938">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_19.png')" x="720" y="682">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_20.png')" x="719" y="937">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_21.png')" x="721" y="1194">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/魔像督军.assets/Image_22.png')" x="720" y="394">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">督军利用盾与剑作一曲<span>消</span><span>愁。演奏过程中，督军会不断散落轻音，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">40%</span><span>伤害；曲终之时拨一重音，声声入耳，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">督军唤出一枚<span textDecoration="underline">谐振器</span><span>，并进行终曲调谐。调谐一完毕，谐振器立即销毁，产生激荡的虹波，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">90%</span><span>伤害。提前摧毁谐振器可以打断督军攻击。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="767" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，督军放下乐器进行追逐，直到目标之处，激奏上挑，造成<span color="#ff9999">70%</span><span>伤害。一般后接「转急促弦」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1023" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，督军怒而一拨，四弦一声如裂帛，出现三刀火刃，均造成<span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="767" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">督军剑指上方，从里向外奏鸣出数个轻音，如数下落，造成<span color="#ff9999">70%,7%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1023" width="435" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">督军置剑于地，从内向外奏响三拍激昂之调，造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害；之后跳起，作曲一拍之终，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">200%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1279" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">督军进行至多2段的多种攻击：跺-盾、跺-切；其中盾、跺、切分别依次造成<span color="#ff9999">60%,70%,80%</span><span>伤害，进行盾攻击之后还会产生音律地波，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">60%,6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">督军进行至多3段的多种攻击：左-右-盾、左-跺-切、左-右-切；其中左、右、盾、跺、切分别依次造成<span color="#ff9999">50%,60%,<br/>60%,70%,80%</span><span>伤害，进行盾攻击之后还会产生音律地波，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">60%,6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#a3320c" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#a3320c">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
