		<RichText x="66" y="1380" width="423" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">白石胄甲：<span color="#ffe599">32岩</span><span>盾，存在时抗性获得提升，击破后瘫痪10s。瘫痪会使其盾量减半，至多减半2次(深渊无此特性)。<br/>谐振器：6次次数盾，击毁可以使白石胄甲-</span><span color="#ffe599">6.4岩</span><span>盾。<br/>福波斯带甲，全抗性提升</span><span color="#ffcebf">100%</span><span>而非80%。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
